Firestore Database	cloud data storage
⚠️ COMMON ERRORS + FIXES
Error	Cause	Fix
Permission denied	restrictive rules	use test mode
Google auth not working	disabled sign-in method	enable Google
Firestore missing	database not created	create Firestore
Wrong region	immutable region selection	choose carefully
